#Approach:

Maximum Nesting Depth of Parentheses – Counter Approach

Is problem me hume batana hota hai ki parentheses kitne maximum level tak nested hain.

Hum ek counter variable rakhte hain jo current depth batata hai.
Jab bhi opening bracket '(' mile, depth 1 se increase kar dete hain
aur maximum depth ko update karte rehte hain.

Jab bhi closing bracket ')' mile, depth 1 se decrease kar dete hain
kyunki ek nesting level close ho gaya.

Baaki characters jaise digits ya operators ko ignore kar dete hain
kyunki unka nesting depth par koi effect nahi hota.

End me jo maximum depth record hui hoti hai,
wahi answer hoti hai.

Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

#Code:

class Solution {
    public int maxDepth(String s) {
        int val = 0;
        int maxLen = 0;

        for(int i=0; i<s.length(); i++){
            if(s.charAt(i) == '('){
                val++;
                maxLen = Math.max(maxLen, val);
            }
            else if(s.charAt(i) == ')'){
                val--;
            }
        }
        return maxLen;
    }
}
